WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.310
Good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:05.269
Lord. Well, I'm back in my spot. I like

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:06.710
to come over here; I like this

00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:09.030
artwork behind us. It's something

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:11.430
different. We do the green screen so

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:13.910
much, and Braden said, "Let's do

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:16.950
a video

00:00:16.950 --> 00:00:16.960
today."Yeah.

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:20.230
So, I'm going to go over some of the

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:23.109
things that the Lord gave us yesterday.

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:24.470
For the ones that didn't watch all the

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:28.230
prayer video, I saw a cone. It went down

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:31.509
like a funnel. And at

00:00:31.519 --> 00:00:33.990
the base of the cone, there was gold.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.389
There were roads

00:00:36.399 --> 00:00:38.709
all around it going to the base.

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:42.869
And there

00:00:42.869 --> 00:00:42.879
were

00:00:42.879 --> 00:00:46.670
18-wheeler rigs that were bringing

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:48.670
gold—pure,

00:00:48.680 --> 00:00:52.630
almost translucent gold—to the

00:00:52.640 --> 00:00:56.310
bottom of this cone. It

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:58.349
had a hole in the middle of it like a

00:00:58.359 --> 00:01:01.110
donut, but it was thick because the

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:03.750
semis were bringing this gold. It

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:07.350
looked identical to the streets of gold in

00:01:07.350 --> 00:01:07.360
heaven, the

00:01:07.360 --> 00:01:09.830
translucence of

00:01:09.830 --> 00:01:09.840
the

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:12.469
gold.

00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:16.550
So, they

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:19.270
were taking this

00:01:19.270 --> 00:01:19.280
gold-like

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:21.830
cement and these trucks

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:24.870
were dumping it into a round circle.

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:27.350
As they were moving down, they were

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:29.109
dumping the gold, and the gold was

00:01:29.119 --> 00:01:31.190
getting thicker and thicker.

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:33.590
I could see the thickness of the

00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:35.630
gold

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:39.190
and a hole in the middle. Now,

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.830
nothing was going through that hole. I

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:43.990
don't know why the hole was there, but

00:01:43.990 --> 00:01:44.000
it

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:46.550
looked like a

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:49.350
black hole and it was completely dark

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:51.030
all the way through. So, there was

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:52.469
nothing coming up and nothing going

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:54.950
down, but it was a cone. I could see

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:57.830
the cone shape; it wasn't

00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:01.749
like a cylinder cone.

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:04.550
It was like a square-looking cone.

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:05.910
I thought that was interesting. It

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:10.389
had four sides at the top

00:02:10.399 --> 00:02:13.110
and it went around all the way up, and it

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:15.030
was a cylinder at the bottom and then went

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:17.110
up like a square at the top, kind of like

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:19.430
a castle, which was very interesting

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.030
because it did not go all the way up

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:24.550
like that. But these semis had silver

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:29.110
beds with white tarps over

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:31.750
the top of them to hide the gold.

00:02:31.750 --> 00:02:31.760
The

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:34.150
semis

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:37.350
had red grills on the front

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:39.509
and

00:02:39.519 --> 00:02:42.710
they were silver semis with red grills

00:02:42.710 --> 00:02:42.720
and

00:02:42.720 --> 00:02:45.030
red front plates, which I thought

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:47.030
was interesting. I try to tell you

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:50.550
more detail as the day goes,

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:53.030
as I'm re-going over

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:55.790
the things and telling y'all.

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:59.270
That was part of the vision. Then

00:03:01.879 --> 00:03:06.790
I saw Ronald Reagan's face

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:12.630
before me. And I saw the old Soviet

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:15.910
Union, the old flag that looked like

00:03:15.920 --> 00:03:17.990
an anchor with the

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:20.309
red and all that for the old

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:22.149
Soviet Union. I could see it in the

00:03:22.159 --> 00:03:25.190
background. I could see the wall, the

00:03:25.190 --> 00:03:25.200
Berlin

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:27.509
wall. "Bring down that

00:03:27.519 --> 00:03:30.309
wall, Gorbachev!"I could see the wall

00:03:30.319 --> 00:03:32.670
and I could see Ronald Reagan's

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:37.830
face. But Trump's face connected to

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.990
Ronald Reagan's face. So, it was half of

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:42.990
Ronald Reagan's face and half of Trump's

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:47.990
face. And as they moved, it was like as

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:50.229
Ronald Reagan's face kind of faded in

00:03:50.239 --> 00:03:53.229
the background, Trump's face came to the

00:03:53.239 --> 00:03:55.509
forefront. I could see his hair

00:03:55.509 --> 00:03:55.519
and

00:03:55.519 --> 00:03:57.110
his eyes. He had the blue

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:59.110
suit on with the white shirt and the red

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:01.670
tie, just like he always does. It was

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:04.309
there and I could see it. But then this

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:06.470
is what's interesting: I could see the

00:04:06.480 --> 00:04:09.670
writing on a wall again behind Trump

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:13.229
that looked like

00:04:17.359 --> 00:04:20.469
graffiti.

00:04:20.479 --> 00:04:22.310
It was graffiti with bubble letters, and it

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:24.310
looked like somebody had really messed

00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:26.230
up the wall behind him.

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:28.469
But it was puffy, bold letters

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:32.070
in

00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:33.749
different fonts.

00:04:33.759 --> 00:04:35.510
It

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:36.950
was behind him, but I couldn't make out

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:39.110
what the bubble letters said; I could

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:41.030
see them behind him, kind of like gang

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:42.550
writing.

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:44.909
And so

00:04:44.919 --> 00:04:50.629
then I saw the design like whenever you see

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:52.790
the old Batman

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:55.749
things like

00:04:55.749 --> 00:04:55.759
"pow,""boom,""bang,"and

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:58.390
they would have

00:05:00.080 --> 00:05:01.670
the explosion design and the words there

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:03.990
whenever they were fighting.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.790
I saw that design

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:10.629
and I heard "Golden Age"as I saw Trump's

00:05:10.639 --> 00:05:13.909
face. I heard "Golden Age."And the Lord

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:16.310
corrected me. He said, "Stop always

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:19.510
thinking you know how big the window

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:22.550
truly is. For I want to make

00:05:22.560 --> 00:05:25.670
this a reward of the wealth of the

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:27.749
sinner laid up for the righteous and for

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:30.070
you to enjoy the wealth that you're

00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:31.990
about to

00:05:31.990 --> 00:05:32.000
receive."He

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:34.310
said, "Brandon, this is a wealth

00:05:34.320 --> 00:05:37.430
transfer for the remnant—the ones that

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:39.150
have listened to me and have

00:05:39.160 --> 00:05:42.790
sacrificially given and sacrificially done

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:45.350
the things that I've called you to do

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:47.310
without

00:05:47.320 --> 00:05:51.189
compromise. You have been right on. And

00:05:51.199 --> 00:05:54.830
I am your exceedingly great

00:05:54.840 --> 00:05:58.390
reward. I am

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:01.830
the El Shaddai, the all-sufficient one.

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:04.150
I supply all your needs. Do you

00:06:04.150 --> 00:06:04.160
understand?"God

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:05.990
is a God that has an

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:08.550
abundant supply. Ladies and gentlemen,

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:10.870
God is not a poor God.

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:12.950
If you

00:06:12.960 --> 00:06:14.950
like poverty, you're certainly not going

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:17.430
to like heaven. There is no poverty in

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:19.670
heaven. There are streets paved with

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:22.390
gold. The foundation has

00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:24.629
rubies, diamonds, sapphires,

00:06:24.639 --> 00:06:26.790
and all the beautiful stones that you

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:28.870
could ever imagine. Folks, I have seen

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:31.029
these visions. I have

00:06:31.039 --> 00:06:33.430
seen what God has prepared for the body

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:36.309
of Christ. If you, being evil, give good

00:06:36.319 --> 00:06:38.469
gifts to your children, how much more

00:06:38.479 --> 00:06:40.390
does your heavenly Father give good

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.710
gifts to those that love him? And I'm

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:44.629
telling you, ladies and gentlemen, God

00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:46.710
has more than enough for you and what's

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:48.950
about to happen and a Golden Age. He

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:52.909
said, "A Golden Age,"and I saw a calendar

00:06:52.919 --> 00:06:56.150
again

00:06:56.150 --> 00:06:56.160
and

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:59.110
a season of blessing for the body of

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:00.550
Christ. Now, you say, "Well,

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:02.550
Brandon, your words kind of

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:04.550
contradict each other. You said you saw

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:06.710
a

00:07:06.710 --> 00:07:06.720
crash."Yes,

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:11.510
I have. But just like

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:14.469
words are given to an audience,

00:07:14.479 --> 00:07:17.110
what is the time frame

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:18.909
that it's supposed to take

00:07:18.919 --> 00:07:22.550
place? Just like Jeremiah

00:07:22.550 --> 00:07:22.560
and

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:26.550
Daniel,

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:28.870
the word that Daniel gave has

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:31.350
still not come to pass. And all

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:32.350
the

00:07:32.360 --> 00:07:36.070
way to John, the same words did not come to

00:07:36.080 --> 00:07:38.309
pass there; we're seeing them manifest

00:07:38.319 --> 00:07:39.909
thousands of years later. And the Lord told

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:41.589
me, "Stop trying to control

00:07:41.589 --> 00:07:41.599
the

00:07:41.599 --> 00:07:44.550
time frame, trying to reason it in

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:46.550
your mind of when you think these things

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:48.029
are going to take

00:07:48.029 --> 00:07:48.039
place."He's

00:07:48.039 --> 00:07:50.150
coming, ladies and

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:53.189
gentlemen. But just like I told you, it

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:55.270
has to come through the vessel, speaking

00:07:55.280 --> 00:07:57.469
it out into existence into the

00:07:57.479 --> 00:08:00.150
atmosphere, just like the

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:02.629
prophets did before Jesus came the first

00:08:02.639 --> 00:08:04.629
time. He said, "Brandon, I'm going to

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:07.350
raise up these words coming up out

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:09.990
of you, for I am decreeing this through

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:12.629
you. You are my voice.

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:14.150
Peace in this earth."That's why he's

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:17.029
saying, "Have a backbone. Say what I say

00:08:17.039 --> 00:08:20.150
to say and walk away from

00:08:20.150 --> 00:08:20.160
it."Decree

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:22.230
and

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:24.629
declare the words that I'm giving you to

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:26.790
tell the people that I'm coming, that the

00:08:26.800 --> 00:08:29.830
sun is setting on the horizon of time

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:33.350
and you have a window.

00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:35.990
Trying to figure out God's timing

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:38.070
whenever a thousand years is a day and a

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.949
day is a thousand years to the

00:08:40.949 --> 00:08:40.959
Lord is

00:08:40.959 --> 00:08:44.470
pretty ignorant, basically,

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:46.150
when we try to put it in our thinking

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:47.750
and go, "Well, God's saying this

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:50.310
and God's saying that,"unless he gives me

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:52.230
a specific saying, well, "Thus saith the

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:54.230
Lord, it's coming on this day at this

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:56.230
hour and this time."Usually, he has

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:58.470
never done that to me; it's usually

00:08:58.480 --> 00:09:01.670
very broad: this is

00:09:01.680 --> 00:09:03.590
what's coming. And you know, it's the

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:05.269
same thing whenever I gave the word

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:07.910
about Trump's ear. I had no idea when

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:11.110
that was going to manifest. I just saw

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:14.070
all that I saw and I told y'all.

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:16.070
I tried to think that it was going to

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:18.070
happen in the summer months, and it did,

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:20.389
because I saw the green grass

00:09:20.389 --> 00:09:20.399
and

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:22.790
the green trees. I saw all those things,

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:24.389
so I knew it wasn't going to come in the

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:28.550
winter because of the fact that

00:09:28.560 --> 00:09:30.630
there's green grass and green trees.

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:34.470
Same thing about the woman that I saw:

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:36.310
she had the French twist in her hair,

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:38.470
she has a ballroom gown, and it will be

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:41.670
at his Mar-al-lago that this lady

00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:43.670
tries to come in there looking

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:46.150
beautiful. She looked like a supermodel

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:48.150
and she was young. She

00:09:48.160 --> 00:09:50.389
walked up to him and she was point-blank at

00:09:50.399 --> 00:09:54.310
his chest. This lady was

00:09:54.320 --> 00:09:55.070
coming

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:57.430
underneath the radar because

00:09:57.440 --> 00:10:00.389
she was gorgeous. Now, why? I have no

00:10:00.399 --> 00:10:02.150
idea. This is the vision that I saw,

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:03.590
and I've already warned about this

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.670
several times. The Lord told me there

00:10:05.670 --> 00:10:05.680
will

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:08.750
be attempts on his life in the

00:10:08.750 --> 00:10:08.760
future—that

00:10:08.760 --> 00:10:12.870
this is not over and that we are

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:15.829
to pray over him continually because of

00:10:15.839 --> 00:10:18.150
what his position holds and what

00:10:18.160 --> 00:10:20.310
God has in store for him. It is not for

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:22.790
him to be taken out by any foreign

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:25.190
adversary. Do you understand? Our job is

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:27.750
to always pray protection over every

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:29.829
political leader and ask God

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:32.470
to intervene and protect. The Lord told

00:10:32.480 --> 00:10:34.630
me a major crash was coming to the

00:10:34.640 --> 00:10:38.550
Chinese economy. We see this;

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:41.750
He warned me about a window that

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:44.389
looked like an open stage

00:10:44.399 --> 00:10:46.230
curtain. You know, whenever you see

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:47.990
those stage curtains with the thick

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:51.269
tapestry, the drapes—the thick

00:10:51.269 --> 00:10:51.279
drapes—but

00:10:51.279 --> 00:10:55.190
it was a red and

00:10:55.190 --> 00:10:55.200
yellow-gold

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:59.190
drape that was just like their flag.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:02.949
There were red drapes and gold

00:11:02.959 --> 00:11:06.389
tassels coming down, and there was a

00:11:06.399 --> 00:11:09.910
golden rope tied in

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:12.470
the center for the drapes of the stage

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:14.870
of the show, like you would see at

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:18.710
a big theater. It was opened

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:21.110
like this, like you're peeking out

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:24.150
of it. It was opened, and it opened up

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:26.710
pretty wide, but the drapes at the top

00:11:26.710 --> 00:11:26.720
were

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:28.310
touching and the drapes at the

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:30.230
bottom were touching. All that was

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:33.110
open was in the middle. I usually

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:35.670
don't go into this kind of detail

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:37.829
whenever I talk because I try to save

00:11:37.839 --> 00:11:41.350
you all time, but this is what I saw.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:43.030
I saw the drape, and the Lord said

00:11:43.040 --> 00:11:45.670
there was an opening coming for the body

00:11:45.680 --> 00:11:49.389
of Christ when this economy

00:11:49.399 --> 00:11:52.069
shakes, and there will be uprising and

00:11:52.079 --> 00:11:53.990
rioting and things happening in the

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:57.430
Chinese community and all of

00:11:57.440 --> 00:12:00.790
China, rising to overthrow the

00:12:00.800 --> 00:12:03.110
government. In this window, I will give

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:06.710
you an opportunity for the gospel to be

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:09.670
preached in all of China, for there will

00:12:09.680 --> 00:12:11.550
be

00:12:11.560 --> 00:12:13.990
distractions. You

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:16.150
understand? With all the economy stuff, there

00:12:16.150 --> 00:12:16.160
are

00:12:16.160 --> 00:12:18.150
distractions. So, people can

00:12:18.160 --> 00:12:21.030
come through that window and minister

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:23.910
the gospel, but it wasn't very big

00:12:23.920 --> 00:12:26.069
and it didn't last a long time. This

00:12:26.079 --> 00:12:27.430
would be the same thing that happens

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:29.990
with North Korea—the same things. Do

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:32.629
you understand? And then remember what I

